author: quark2
body:
#### PR description:
We've added two classes of plots for the GEM onlineDQM: One is a new representation of VFAT electronics status as a function of chamber vs. VFAT while the other class is a wheel occupancy of recHits.

This is a backport of #33767 to CMSSW_11_3_X

#### PR validation:
Test are done and one can check again by `runTheMatrix` workflows

@jshlee @watson-ij @hyunyong
title: new VFAT status plots and recHit wheel occupancy plots on GEM onlineDQM, a backport to CMSSW_11_3_X
